data.title: S07.s1 - Exercises: A. Fill in The Blanks With The Right Forms of The Verbs in Brackets
data.meta_description: S06 ejercicios - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Jimmy and Paul went camping in the mountains last Easter holidays. They spent a wonderful time hiking, buying supplies in the village, playing football, watching birds, and swimming in the river. In the evening, with no TV, they talked and then went to sleep. The document then provides sample conversations and questions to practice past tenses and asks the reader to describe their busy day yesterday using past tense verbs.
